dropins.contents:
[Unit]
Requires=coreos-metadata.service
After=coreos-metadata.service

[Service]
EnvironmentFile=/run/metadata/coreos
Environment="ETCD_IMAGE_TAG=v3.0.15"
ExecStart=
ExecStart=/usr/lib/coreos/etcd-wrapper $ETCD_OPTS \
  --name="${COREOS_EC2_HOSTNAME}" \
  --listen-peer-urls="http://${COREOS_EC2_IPV4_LOCAL}:2380" \
  --listen-client-urls="http://0.0.0.0:2379" \
  --initial-advertise-peer-urls="http://${COREOS_EC2_IPV4_LOCAL}:2380" \
  --initial-cluster="${COREOS_EC2_HOSTNAME}=http://${COREOS_EC2_IPV4_LOCAL}:2380" \
  --advertise-client-urls="http://${COREOS_EC2_IPV4_LOCAL}:2379" \
  --discovery="https://discovery.etcd.io/c44d0693351db89c6539e7ec8888a280"
dropins.name: 20-clct-etcd-member.conf

units.contents:
[Unit]
Description=Docker Socket for the API

[Socket]
ListenStream=2375
Service=docker.service
BindIPv6Only=both

[Install]
WantedBy=sockets.target
units.name: docker-tcp.socket
